==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chirography
<hw>Chi*rog"ra*phy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
art of writing or engrossing; handwriting; <as>as, skilled in
<ex>chirography</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The art of telling fortunes by examining the
hand.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chirogymnast</ent>⟦br⟧
